{"tid":2014991,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳彥祖不滿特朗普言論　IG轉發帖文：你不能為我們發言","createTime":"2020-05-13T11:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T11:56:58.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"04ac408c53a04c0528c3581846516886effc5bb2","tid":2014991,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:00:35.000Z","msg":"雖然肺炎疫情在香港有緩和跡象，但全球每日的確診數字仍然高企，美國疫情仍然嚴峻。美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）曾公開表示病毒來自中國，他於5月12日在Twitter表示，亞裔美國人對中國對美方和全世界所做的事情感到「非常憤怒」，擁有美國國籍的吳彥祖在社交網站專發特朗普帖文截圖，並指其言論不代表他們。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在帖文表示，亞裔美國人對中國向美方和全世界所做的事情感到非常憤怒，尤其美籍華人是最為憤怒的，而他自己並不責怪這些美籍華人。在美國土生土長的吳彥祖，在IG轉發特朗普這則帖文，並以英文留言說：「你不能為我們發言。」表示不同意對方言論。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普早前稱呼新冠狀病毒為「Chinese virus」，美籍藝人陳法拉於3月17日在社交網站鬧爆相關言論歧視中國人：「「Why does he have even the energy to make up s**t like that, when we have so much to deal with and to heal from!?!?!? This is intentional racist.（為什麼他還有精力編造出這種鬼話呢，在我們還有這麼多事情需要處理和需要治療的這種時候？這是有意的種族歧視。）」當時引起不少爭議。"},{"pid":"5639a2338646bc9c3d8a75836e8fc8fb1cbe859e","tid":2014991,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4481736/org/f3959b5cbd10693134d06478b56d8df4.jpeg/iaQ46emG2e0mZ_eaHjta-_5MVZIPZPkI4k7cluJO3JY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4481736%2Forg%2Ff3959b5cbd10693134d06478b56d8df4.jpeg%2FiaQ46emG2e0mZ_eaHjta-_5MVZIPZPkI4k7cluJO3JY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=efc61b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳彥祖在IG轉發特朗普的帖文，並表示不同意其言論，認為對方沒有權利為美籍華人發言。（IG截圖片／thatdanielwu）"},{"pid":"5eda37b9cf0e23e2567809b6e446744c4824a464","tid":2014991,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4182198/org/fdbf80a87fa3fb32ce86a7ab9d1adbd9.jpg/PNyo1aaRdQ5-t93ztEER23uME1i2t7jHKLWmhyi1poc?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4182198%2Forg%2Ffdbf80a87fa3fb32ce86a7ab9d1adbd9.jpg%2FPNyo1aaRdQ5-t93ztEER23uME1i2t7jHKLWmhyi1poc%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=7813a174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳法拉早前亦曾在IG上鬧爆美國總統特朗普。（IG圖片／falachenfala）"},{"pid":"980c21eb80eecb5c2b341021601f8a26a2eaa897","tid":2014991,"uid":132174,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:03:48.000Z","msg":"Trump 出聲想美國佬唔歧視你班chigga 你就唔領情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dad8cc0e798ed17a49c1fb2a3ede9d212534485","tid":2014991,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:17:38.000Z","msg":"連登仔幾時一齊上ig 一人一句 你不能為我們發言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eca60c21985a71707f820877d34ea2660035466","tid":2014991,"uid":86727,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:28:16.000Z","msg":"美國總統不能為美國人發聲，哪誰能???"},{"pid":"31b85f6d9e9e889dec5e1f9d084ab8a3f6f1a407","tid":2014991,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dad8cc0e798ed17a49c1fb2a3ede9d212534485","tid":2014991,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:17:38.000Z","msg":"連登仔幾時一齊上ig 一人一句 你不能為我們發言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:40:00.000Z","msg":"上微博鬧口交部<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8a627658e8be5e4fdce2236f4a8ee2ce7a1ca4","tid":2014991,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T11:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zAE9qKY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzAE9qKY.gif&h=90ed3a88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09bc734228ff033e08c7ea15448afe8c12b91fc1","tid":2014991,"uid":170044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eca60c21985a71707f820877d34ea2660035466","tid":2014991,"uid":86727,"like":1,"dislike":1